ADDITIONAL FOOD, RESTAURANT & DELIVERY DISCLAIMER

This software is a technical demonstration of conversational AI patterns for
food ordering and delivery use cases. It is NOT:

  • A real food delivery service or restaurant aggregator
  • An FSSAI-licensed food business operator
  • Connected to any real restaurant, kitchen, payment gateway, or delivery
    network

The included data (restaurants, menus, dish prices, allergen tags, RERA-style
identifiers, riders, addresses, offers) is entirely FICTIONAL. Restaurant
names like Saffron Kitchen, Green Bowl Co., and Slice Society are invented
brands and do not correspond to any real establishment.

THE ALLERGEN SAFETY LAYER IS BEST-EFFORT AND CANNOT VERIFY KITCHEN-LEVEL
SAFETY. Menu allergen tags reflect only the ingredients explicitly listed by
the source data. Real-world allergens travel through:

  • Cross-contamination from shared cooking surfaces, oils, knives, utensils
  • Hidden ingredients not always disclosed by restaurants
  • Stock-rotation and substitution at the kitchen's discretion
  • Trace exposure during plating and packaging

No software — including this one — can verify what's actually happening in
a restaurant's kitchen. If you have a SEVERE or LIFE-THREATENING food allergy
(anaphylaxis risk), this demo's allergen filters are NOT a safe substitute
for calling the restaurant, reviewing their published allergen statement,
and confirming preparation procedures directly with the chef.

EMI-style offer math (FIRSTBITE 50% up to ₹150, BOWLSAVE 20% on Green Bowl,
DESSERT100 flat ₹100 off) is illustrative. Real offer terms vary by platform.

Age-gating for alcohol is acknowledged but not enforced — Gujarat is a dry
state where alcohol delivery is restricted. India's legal drinking age
varies by state (18–25). Real platforms enforce ID verification at handover.

Payment privacy: this demo refuses to accept card numbers / CVV / OTP / PIN
through chat. Real payment flows must use PCI-DSS-compliant encrypted
gateways with explicit user consent — chat is never an appropriate channel
for payment instrument data.

Do not deploy this software as a real food delivery platform without
substantial modification, FSSAI compliance, qualified review of the allergen
disclosure system by a registered dietitian or food-safety professional, and
proper payment-gateway integration with a PCI-DSS-certified provider.
